0our%20lives%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-make-friends-as-adult-moving-cities-nyc-la-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ebecame%20friends%20with%20each%20other%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20was%20relaxed%2C%20delightful%2C%20and%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20best%20things%20I've%20done%20for%20my%20social%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20was%20the%20first%20iteration%20of%20the%20Monthly%20Party%20(MP)%2C%20our%20recurring%20open-house%20gathering%20that%20removes%20the%20implicit%20pressure%20of%20more%20formal%20or%20less%20frequent%20events.%20If%20you%20miss%20one%20MP%2C%20no%20big%20deal%3B%20there%20will%20be%20another.%20If%20you%20don't%20know%20if%20you'll%20feel%20like%20socializing%20that%20day%2C%20cool%3B%20just%20decide%20the%20day%20of.%20There's%20no%20itinerary%2C%20no%20structure%2C%20just%20a%20good%20old-fashioned%20%3Cem%3Ehang%3C%2Fem%3E.%20It%20requires%20little%20else%20from%20me%20except%20sending%20an%20email%20a%20few%20weeks%20before%20each%20MP%20to%20set%20the%20date.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224cf632c2-0f84-46a7-b88f-a6cf11b72669%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EEveryone%20just%20wants%20to%20hang%20out%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20was%20inspired%20to%20kick%20off%20our%20MP%20by%20my%20friend%20Stephanie%20Logan%2C%20who%20has%20hosted%20an%20interview%20podcast%20and%20spoken%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRb7o0CveVAU%26ab_channel%3DTEDxTalks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eon%20connection%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20Along%20with%20MPs%2C%20she%20and%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%20also%20host%20an%20annual%20summer%20camp%20takeover%20for%20all%20their%20friends.%20I%20asked%20her%20why%20she%20started%20her%20MPs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20so%20sick%20of%20texting%20everyone%20and%20making%20Doodle%20polls%20to%20try%20to%20find%20a%20good%20time%20and%20then%20running%20myself%20ragged%20trying%20to%20be%20a%20picturesque%20host%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BMonthly%20Party%20works%20because%20we%20just%20pick%20a%20day%2C%20and%20whoever%20can%20come%20shows%20up%20with%20no%20obligation%20to%20dress%20up%20or%20bring%20a%20themed%20dish%2C%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjudged-daughter-not-folding-laundry-cleaning-parenting-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ehouse%20doesn't%20have%20to%20be%20spotless%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20everyone%20just%20gets%20to%20hang%20out%2C%20which%20is%20why%20we%20all%20want%20to%20go%20to%20a%20party%20anyway.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20true%20%E2%80%94%20don't%20we%20all%20just%20want%20to%20hang%20out%3F%20Much%20has%20been%20written%20about%20how%20people%20are%20lonelier%2C%20spend%20less%20time%20together%2C%20and%20have%20a%20harder%20time%20making%20friends.%20A%20recent%20article%20in%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Ffamily%2Farchive%2F2025%2F01%2Fthrow-more-parties-loneliness%2F681203%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Atlantic%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BAmericans%20Need%20to%20Party%20More%2C%26quot%3B%20offered%20a%20proposed%20solution%20and%20hit%20a%20nerve%20online%3B%20I%20saw%20some%20social%20media%20chatter%20in%20response%20about%20how%20it's%20too%20hard%20to%20party%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20space%20or%20expense.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20need%20to%20rethink%20what%20a%20party%20has%20to%20be%2C%20from%20what%20should%20be%20brought%20to%20one%20to%20the%20proper%20space%20for%20hosting.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-of-five-lives-small-apartment-prefers-over-big-house-2024-11%5