's%20decadelong%20war.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-unilaterally-release-153-war-detainees-red-cross-says%2Farticleshow%2F117552072.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-unilaterally-release-153-war-detainees-red-cross-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F117552072.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fyemens-houthi-rebels-unilaterally-release-153-war-detainees-red-cross-says%2Famp_articleshow%2F117552072.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%202025%3A%20What%20Changes%20Do%20Economists%20Suggest%20For%20Salaried%20Taxpayers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEvery%20Budget%20season%2C%20the%20most-asked%20question%20remains%20the%20same%20-%20does%20it%20have%20anything%20for%20the%20salaried%20class%3F%20With%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20set%20to%20present%20Budget%202025-26%20on%20February%201%2C%20the%20salaried%20class%20is%20again%20looking%20out%20if%20the%20government%20has%20any%20plans%20to%20reduce%20their%20financial%20burden.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEconomists%20have%20suggested%20that%20the%20government%20this%20time%20offer%20a%20higher%20tax%20exemption%20limit%20and%20an%20increased%20standard%20deduction%20under%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%20which%20would%20benefit%20a%20lot%20of%20taxpayers.%20In%20the%20last%20Budget%2C%20the%20standard%20deduction%20was%20increased%20to%20Rs%2075%2C000%20from%20Rs%2050%2C000%20while%20the%20exemption%20limit%20stands%20at%20Rs%203%20lakh%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20economists%20also%20hinted%20at%20tax%20benefits%20for%20electric%20vehicles%2C%20boosting%20the%20housing%20sector%2C%20and%20easing%20the%20purchase%20and%20sale%20of%20real%20estate%20by%20Non-Residential%20Indians%20(NRIs).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeepika%20Mathur%2C%20Director%20at%20Deloitte%20India%2C%20said%20that%20if%20the%20government%20plans%20to%20offer%20any%20relief%20to%20the%20salaried%20class%20at%20all%2C%20it%20may%20benefit%20only%20those%20under%20the%20new%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20really%20do%20not%20expect%20any%20changes%20in%20the%20old%20tax%20regime.%20However%2C%20I%20do%20expect%20a%20further%20increase%20in%20the%20standard%20deduction%20in%20the%20new%20tax%20regime.%20Whatever%20changes%20will%20happen%2C%20whether%20an%20increase%20in%20standard%20deduction%20or%20a%20change%20in%20tax%20rate%20or%20slab%20if%20at%20all%20or%20enhancement%20of%20basic%20exemption%20limit%2C%20I%20expect%20for%20it%20to%20happen%20in%20the%20new%20tax%20regime%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20regime%20simplifies%20tax%20filing%20and%20offers%20lower%20tax%20rates%2C%20but%20unlike%20the%20old%20regime%2C%20it%20does%20not%20offer%20deductions.%20On%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20the%20old%20regime%20offers%20a%20slew%20of%20deductions%20but%20also%20comes%20with%20higher%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20inflation%20eating%20away%20the%20worth%20of%20money%2C%20consumers%20are%20also%20keen%20on%20efforts%20that%20would%20increase%20the%20purchasing%20powers%20of%20the%20middle%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWeighing%20in%2C%20Sanchita%20Mukherji%2C%20Senior%20Business%20Economist%20and%20Managing%20Partner%20at%20'Talk%20The%20Walk'%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20salaried%20individuals%20are%20taxed%20disproportionately.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20India%2C%20the%20middle-class%20salaried%20individuals%20pay%20a%20disproportionately%20high%20personal%20income%20tax%20as%20salaries%20are%20taxed%20far%20more%20easily%20than%20any%20other%20kind%20of%20income.%20The%20complaint%20is%20that%20the%20middle%20class%2C%20which%20first%20pays%20tax%20from%20income%2C%20are%20taxed%20again%20while%20spending%20post-tax%20income%20and%20capital%20gains%20from%20the%20sale%20of%20shares%20and%20property%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20key%20challenge%20that%20Ms%20Mathur%20believes%20the%20government%20should%20address%20in%20this%20year's%20Budget%20is%20facilitating%20tax%20payments%20from%20overseas%20bank%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20overseas%2C%20they%20are%20foreign%20nationals%2C%20Indians%20or%20Non-Resident%20Indians%2C%20who%20may%20have%20worked%20in%20the%20past%20or%20are%20overseas%20and%20have%20investment%20income%20in%20India.%20The%20payments%20can%20be%20made%20for%20taxes%20only%20from%20an%20Indian%20bank%20account.%20Sometimes%20that's%20a%20challenge%2C%20so%20tax%20payments%20should%20be%20facilitated%20from%20overseas%20bank%20accounts%20because%20the%20government%20is%20concerned%20with%20having%20the%20tax%20payout%20without%20many%20compliance%20issues.%20Therefore%2C%20it%20should%20not%20be%20relevant%20where%20the%20payment%20is%20coming%20from%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20an%20Indian%20bank%20account%20or%20an%20overseas%20bank%20account%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20these%20are%20proposed%20measures%2C%20the%20spotlight%20is%20on%20whether%20February%201%20will%20transform%20the%20taxation%20landscape%20in%20India%20altogether%20or%20will%20the%20middle%20class%20be%20left%20craving%20for%20more%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737801180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8ponno68_budget-2025_625x300_22_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-2025-what-changes-do-economists-suggest-for-salaried-taxpayers-7556365%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20set%20to%20present%20Union%20Budget%202025-26%20on%20February%201%2C%20the%20salaried%20class%20is%20again%20looking%20out%20if%20the%20government%20has%20any%20plans%20to%20reduce%20their%20financial%20burden.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22DLF%20sells%20173%20ultra%20luxury%20apartments%20for%20Rs%2011%2C816%20cr%20in%20Gurugram%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737801039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdlf-sells-173-ultra-luxury-apartments-for-rs-11-816-cr-in-gurugram-125012500609_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20October%20last%20year%2C%20DLF%20launched%20a%2017-acre%20housing%20project%20'The%20Dahlias'%20at%20DLF%20Phase%205%20in%20Gurugram%2C%20Haryana%20comprising%20420%20apartments%20and%20penthouses%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22An%20engineer's%20hobby%20trading%20stocks%20returned%20308%25%20in%202024.%20Here's%20how%20he%20identifies%20top-quality%20names.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22653%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mohamed%20Gad%2C%20stock%20trader.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792b39eae09223df2bb4f7c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22411%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMohamed%20Gad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMohamed%20Gad%20shares%20the%20lessons%20learned%20on%20his%20journey%20to%20becoming%20a%20part-time%20swing%20trader.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20emphasizes%20seeking%20high-quality%20and%20high-growth%20stocks%2C%20focusing%20on%20earnings%20and%20sales.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAnd%2C%20he%20shares%20his%20minimum%20thresholds%20for%20daily%20volume%20traded%20and%20stock%20price.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Mohamed%20Gad%20started%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fstock-trading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etrading%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019%2C%20he%20was%20cautiously%20optimistic%20after%20a%20failed%20attempt%20five%20years%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20first%20rodeo%20was%20in%202014%20when%20he%20jumped%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fwhat-are-penny-stocks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epenny-stock%20trading%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20%241%2C000%20but%20blew%20himself%20out%20of%20the%20market%20after%20just%20a%20week.%20The%20short-lived%20experience%20led%20him%20to%20conclude%20it%20wasn't%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20a%20spell%20of%20boredom%20in%202019%20would%20cause%20him%20to%20reconsider.%20Wondering%20whether%20there%20was%20a%20better%20way%2C%20he%20began%20seeking%20out%20any%20information%20he%20could%20about%20how%20to%20trade%20steadily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20ended%20up%20pretty%20much%20reading%20every%20trading%20book%20known%20to%20man%2C%26quot%3B%20Gad%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20attended%20a%20few%20sessions%20here%20and%20there.%20Some%20of%20those%20I%20learned%20a%20lot%20from%2C%20others%20I%20think%20it's%20one%20of%20those%2C%20'I'm%20trying%20to%20sell%20you%20a%20course'%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20wasn't%20until%20he%20came%20across%20William%20O'Neil's%20series%20of%20books%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20to%20Make%20Money%20in%20Stocks%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20something%20finally%20clicked%20for%20him.%20The%20methodology%2C%20built%20around%20a%20focus%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fhow-to-buy-stock%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigh-quality%20and%20high-growth%20stocks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20was%20a%20welcomed%20discovery.%20It%20emphasized%20seeking%20companies%20with%20solid%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Feps%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearnings%20and%20sales%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20meant%20he'd%20be%20investing%20in%20names%20with%20sturdier%20fundamentals%20rather%20than%20gambling%20on%20unknown%20tickers.%20He%20could%20also%20focus%20on%20his%20day%20job%20and%20sleep%20well%20at%20night%20without%20waking%20up%20to%20a%20position%20that%20was%20wiped%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20newfound%20understanding%20was%20eventually%20met%20with%20the%20pandemic%20and%20the%20world%20shutdown%2C%20giving%20him%20time%20to%20review%20data%20and%20charts%20while%20testing%20some%20trades.%20That%20year%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Findex%2Fs%26amp%3Bp_500%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ES%26amp%3BP%20500%3C%2Fa%3E%20had%20a%20good%20run%2C%20finishing%20with%20a%2016.3%25%20return.%20He%20told%20Business%20Insider%20he%20made%20a%20175%25%20gain%2C%20with%20Tesla%20being%20one%20of%20his%20biggest%20winners.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20thought%20I%20was%20a%20genius.%20I%20figured%20this%20out.%20I%20can%20quit%20my%20job%20and%20do%20this%20for%20a%20living.%20It's%20easy%2C%26quot%3B%20Gad%20said.%20He%20wasn't%20alone%3A%202020%20brought%20a%20surge%20of%20new%20retail%20investors%2C%20but%20many%20were%20chasing%20hype%20without%20direction%20and%20were%20met%20with%20a%20rude%20awakening.%20The%20last%20quarter%20of%202021%20brought%20a%20steep%20pullback%20that%20would%20extend%20to%20a%20yearlong%20decline%20in%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500.%20Gad%20began%20taking%20large%20losses%2C%20especially%20on%20his%20favorite%20stock%2C%20Tesla%2C%20a%20position%20he%20held%20onto%20because%20he%20loved%20the%20company.%20But%20by%20October%202022%2C%20he%20realized%20it%20was%20unwise%20and%20estimated%20losing%20about%2075%25%20of%20his%20previous%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20began%20finetuning%20his%20strategy%2C%20tightening%20his%20entry%20and%20exit%20ranges%2C%20and%20being%20more%20intentional%20about%20how%20he%20filters%20for%20stocks.%20A%20book%20by%20US%20Investing%20Champion%20Oliver%20Kell%2C%20%26quot%3BVictory%20in%20Stock%20Trading%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20some%20finishing%20touches%20to%20his%20strategy%2C%20mainly%20removing%20emotional%20attachments%20to%20companies%20and%20viewing%20each%20position%20as%20merely%20a%20ticker%20on%20a%20chart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20there%20on%2C%20it%20would%20be%20all%20about%20reviewing%20historical%20data%20to%20help%20gauge%20future%20price%20swings%20and%20patterns%2C%20and%20being%20comfortable%20exiting%20when%20necessary%2C%20even%20if%20that%20meant%20selling%20Tesla.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%202024%2C%20he%20felt%20stable%20enough%20to%20test%20his%20skills%20in%20the%20US%20Investing%20Championship%2C%20an%20annual%20contest%20for%20retail%20traders%20run%20by%20former%20math%20professor%20Norman%20Zadeh.%20He%20entered%20the%20competition%20in%20May%20after%20returning%20from%20a%20work%20trip%20and%20completed%20a%20stock%20division%20challenge%20up%20by%20308%25%20between%20May%20to%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227109e995-888b-4618-ad70-7f92c5eada4a%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ECore%20strategy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrading%20strategies%20are%20like%20fingerprints.%20On%20the%20surface%2C%20they%20can%20look%20similar%2C%20but%20each%20trader%20has%20their%20own%20finishing%20touches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20Gad%2C%20a%20petroleum%20and%20subsea%20engineer%2C%20travels%20for%20work%20and%20has%20long%20hours%2C%20sometimes%20offshore%2C%20he%20doesn't%20have%20time%20to%20day%20trade%20or%20filter%20for%20stocks%20regularly.%20The%20longer%20hold%20periods%20suit%20his%20schedule.%20However%2C%20it%20also%20means%20he%20can't%20trade%20every%20stock%20that%20meets%20his%20criteria.%20So%2C%20he%20spends%20a%20few%20days%20a%20week%20checking%20his%20positions%20and%20determining%20whether%20he%20needs%20to%20reshuffle%20any.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20he%20needs%20stocks%20that%20can%20be%20held%20for%20weeks%20to%20months%20without%20being%20stopped%20out%20by%20a%20stop%20loss.%20Two%20key%20factors%20must%20be%20in%20place%20to%20achieve%20this%3A%20lower%20volatility%20and%20momentum%20with%20an%20entry%20point%20that%20gives%20a%20stock%20room%20to%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20that%20staying%20within%20certain%20ranges%20helps%20achieve%20some%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20he%20sticks%20to%20stocks%20with%20a%20minimum%20daily%20volume%20of%20300%2C000%20shares%20traded%20to%20maintain%20liquidity%20and%20a%20share%20price%20above%20%2420.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20momentum%2C%20he%20seeks%20stocks%20that%20have%20been%20on%20an%20uptrend%20with%20a%20minimum%20increase%20of%2020%25%20over%20the%20previous%20one%20to%20three%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20simple%20requirements%20still%20leave%20him%20with%20many%20tickers.%20To%20narrow%20it%20further%2C%20he%20focuses%20on%20the%20stocks%20held%20up%20by%20stronger%20fundamentals.%20Specifically%2C%20companies%20that%20have%20expectations%20for%20high%20future%20growth%2C%20which%20means%20earnings%20and%20sales%20estimates%20above%2010%25.%20Here%2C%20he%20favors%20those%20with%20the%20highest%20consensus%20estimates%2C%20often%20above%2030%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20go%20through%20the%20fundamentals%2C%20this%20is%20where%20I%20can%20identify%20the%20top-quality%20names%20that%20I%20would%20focus%20on%2C%26quot%3B%20Gad%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20can%20put%20five%20to%20six%20names%20and%20stick%20to%20them%20the%20entire%20year.%20I%20might%20be%20taking%20some%20paper%20cuts%20here%20and%20there%20and%20some%20gains%20here%20and%20there%2C%20but%20when%20these%20start%20moving%2C%20it%20can%20move%20the%20needle.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20table%20below%20shows%20how%20volatile%20earnings%20per%20share%20and%20sales%20estimates%20are%2C%20even%20for%20a%20large-cap%20stock%20like%20Tesla%20(TSLA).%20His%20initial%20approach%20would%20have%20meant%20holding%20through%20the%20negative%20estimates.%20Now%2C%20he%20can%20follow%20the%20data%20and%20take%20profits%20when%20necessary.%20For%20example%2C%20Gad%20took%20a%20very%20large%20position%20in%20Tesla%20in%20June%202024%2C%20which%20made%20up%20over%2087%25%20of%20his%20portfolio%20for%20that%20month%2C%20just%20as%20the%20earnings%20were%20expected%20to%20turn%20the%20corner%20into%20positive%20territory%2C%20according%20to%20statements%20from%20his%20brokerage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22670%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Table%20of%20Tesla%20earnings%20and%20sales.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793d70b2fcded5e9074a220%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22356%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMarketSurge.%20Investor%20Business%20Daily.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20Gad's%20strategy%2C%20while%20it%20has%20some%20solid%20methodologies%2C%20isn't%20one%20with%20a%20high%20win%20ratio.%20His%20winners%20to%20losers%20sit%20at%2030%2F70%2C%20which%20means%20his%20losses%20are%20substantially%20higher.%20He%20blames%20overtrading%20or%20entering%20a%20position%20when%20the%20stock%20is%20overextended%20after%20a%20breakout%2C%20a%20sudden%20move%20to%20the%20upside%20often%20followed%20by%20a%20pullback.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20limit%20his%20position%20sizing%20as%20part%20of%20his%20risk%20management%20tool%2C%20a%20commonly%20used%20practice.%20But%20he%20does%20use%20a%20stop-loss%20that%20moves%20along%20the%2021-moving%20day%20average.%20A%20low%20win%20ratio%20means%20the%20gains%20for%20each%20winner%20need%20to%20outpace%20multiple%20smaller%20losses%2C%20which%20he%20incurs%20from%20a%20stop%20loss%20that%20limits%20the%20margin%20of%20each%20loss.%20Meanwhile%2C%20he%20allows%20his%20winners%20to%20run.%20Once%20the%20stock%20has%20run%20up%20enough%2C%20he%20will%20zoom%20out%20and%20use%20the%20weekly%20charts%20to%20set%20stop%20losses%20along%20more%20significant%20areas%20on%20the%20chart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20core%20of%20Gad's%20strategy%20is%20built%20on%20the%20above%20methods%2C%20he%20also%20uses%20technical%20analysis%20to%20determine%20the%20best%20entry%20points%20for%20each%20stock.%20Additionally%2C%20not%20all%20of%20Gad's%202024%20gains%20resulted%20from%20the%20above%20strategy.%20He%20also%20made%20significant%20gains%20from%20MicroStrategy%20and%20the%20iShares%20Bitcoin%20Trust%20ETF%20due%20to%20his%20strong%20conviction%20in%20bitcoin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-trade-stocks-trader-high-returns-best-strategy-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737801001000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6793d8ac2fcded5e9074a271%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-trade-stocks-trader-high-returns-best-strategy-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20stock%20must%20meet%20two%20key%20thresholds%20and%20outperform%20on%20two%20multiples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmaidan%40businessinsider.com%20(Laila%20Maidan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-trade-stocks-trader-high-returns-best-strategy-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine's%20Kursk%20invasion%20was%20a%20risky%20play%2C%20but%20it%20might%20have%20nailed%20the%20timing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20a%20video%20shows%20a%20missile%20firing%20from%20the%20back%20of%20a%20vehicle%2C%20sparking%20flames%20at%20nighttime%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67927310ae09223df2bb3fd4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221125%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20still%20from%20a%20video%20that%20was%20released%20by%20the%20Russian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20shows%20a%20Russian%20%26quot%3BGrad%26quot%3B%20self-propelled%20multiple%20rocket%20launcher%20firing%20towards%20Ukrainian%20positions%20in%20Russia's%20Kursk%20region.%3Cp%3ERussian%20Defense%20Ministry%20Press%20Service%20via%20AP%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20took%20a%20huge%20risk%20attacking%20into%20Russia%20and%20taking%20territory%20last%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20has%20had%20positives%20and%20negatives%20for%20both%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20if%20it%20still%20holds%20enough%20of%20the%20territory%20as%20Trump%20pushes%20for%20negotiations%20it%20could%20pay%20off.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20risky%20gamble%20to%20seize%20Russian%20territory%20could%20ultimately%20pay%20off%2C%20if%20for%20no%20other%20reason%20than%20the%20timing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20forces%20rolled%20the%20dice%20on%20a%20gamble%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-does-ukraine-want-with-attack-on-kursk-russia-goals-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadvanced%20into%20the%20Russian%20region%20of%20Kursk%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20August.%20They%20opted%20to%20use%20precious%20manpower%20and%20weaponry%20in%20a%20bold%20play%20to%20divert%20Russian%20resources%2C%20create%20a%20buffer%20zone%2C%20seize%20the%20momentum%2C%20and%20take%20land%20and%20prisoners%20that%20could%20be%20exchanged%20in%20future%20negotiations.%20The%20move%20into%20Kursk%20was%20a%20shocking%20development%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUkraine%20war%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20front%20lines%20of%20which%20had%20been%20static%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwas-ukraine-risky-attack-of-russias-kursk-region-worth-it-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresults%20of%20the%20surprise%20incursion%20have%20been%20mixed%3C%2Fa%3E.%20While%20war%20experts%20have%20said%20it%20was%20a%20reasonable%20call%20given%20the%20morale%20and%20momentum%20wins%2C%20as%20well%20as%20the%20upsetting%20of%20Russia's%20war%20plans%2C%20the%20move%20hasn't%20significantly%20relieved%20pressure%20on%20the%20front%20lines%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20the%20Ukrainians%20have%20struggled%20to%20hold%20a%20lot%20of%20what%20they%20captured.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20setbacks%2C%20the%20timing%20of%20this%20thing%20could%20make%20it%20worthwhile.%20Right%20now%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20holding%20Russian%20territory%20amid%20a%20new%20push%20to%20end%20the%20war%20through%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhoever%20holds%20territory%20in%20Kursk%20%26quot%3Bis%20going%20to%20be%20in%20the%20box%20seat%20for%20any%20ceasefire%20negotiations%2C%26quot%3B%20Col.%20Hamish%20de%20Bretton-Gordon%2C%20a%20defense%20expert%20and%20a%20former%20commander%20for%20the%20UK's%20Joint%20Chemical%2C%20Biological%2C%20Radiological%2C%20and%20Nuclear%20forces%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a382771-cf03-49e1-af56-d6e1af469cc9%5C%22%3ENew%20talk%20of%20negotiations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETim%20Willasey-Wilsey%2C%20a%20conflict%20resolution%20expert%20at%20King's%20College%20London%20and%20a%20former%20British%20diplomat%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.npr.org%2F2025%2F01%2F16%2Fnx-s1-5258183%2Fukraine-russia-trump-peace%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0this%20month%20that%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20Kursk%20operation%20was%20%26quot%3Bquite%20deliberate%26quot%3B%20because%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btrying%20to%20take%20some%20territory%20which%20could%20lead%20to%20bargaining.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20now%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-wins-presidential-election-race-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETrump's%20re-election%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20created%20new%20talk%20of%20efforts%20to%20revolve%20the%20war%20through%20negotiations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20repeatedly%20said%20that%20he%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-trump-picks-mean-for-ukraine-skepticism-time-pressure-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eend%20the%20war%20through%20negotiations%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20week%2C%20he%20said%20he%20would%20put%20more%20economic%20pressure%20on%20Russia%20to%20get%20it%20to%20make%20a%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy%20has%20also%20signaled%20an%20increased%20willingness%20to%20enter%20talks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelenskyy%20said%20in%20November%20the%20parts%20of%20Ukraine%20still%20under%20its%20own%20control%20could%20be%20taken%20%26quot%3Bunder%20the%20NATO%20umbrella%26quot%3B%20as%20part%20of%20an%20agreement%20that%20still%20holds%20Ukraine's%20borders%20as%20its%20internationally%20recognized%20borders.%20He%20said%20Ukraine%20could%20then%20negotiate%20the%20return%20of%20its%20own%20territory%20that%20was%20still%20under%20Russian%20control%20%26quot%3Bin%20a%20diplomatic%20way.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDe%20Bretton-Gordon%20said%20Zelenskyy's%20comments%20reinforce%20that%20%26quot%3BKursk%20is%20absolutely%20key.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20%26quot%3Bvictory%20plan%26quot%3B%20Zelenskyy%20unveiled%20in%20October%20also%20called%20for%20the%20continuation%20of%20Ukraine's%20work%20in%20Kursk%2C%20hinting%20at%20its%20value.%20De%20Bretton-Gordon%20said%20it%20shows%20Zelenskyy%20may%20be%20seeing%20Kursk%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20key%20bargaining%20chip.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMark%20Cancian%2C%20a%20senior%20advisor%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20given%20Trump%20is%20%26quot%3Balmost%20certain%26quot%3B%20to%20push%20negotiations%2C%20%26quot%3Bit's%20good%20to%20have%20this%20bargaining%20chip.%26quot%3B%20Plus%2C%20he%20said%2C%20negotiations%20are%20likely%20to%20take%20place%20sooner%20than%20they%20would%20have%20under%20a%20Kamala%20Harris%20presidency%2C%20making%20it%20more