think%20they%20were%20excited%20and%20proud%20of%20me%20for%20studying%20finance%2C%20graduating%2C%20and%20landing%20a%20job%20like%20this.%20But%20that%20path%20didn't%20last%20for%20long.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22018193d3-8ded-46d8-88ac-f94c2d66dc0a%5C%22%3EI%20hated%20the%20exhausting%20hustle%20culture%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20working%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbig-four-consultancies-leaders-pwc-deloitte-ey-kpmg-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDeloitte%3C%2Fa%3E%20full-time%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202008%20after%20graduating.%20My%20job%20required%20extremely%20long%20hours%20in%20what%20was%20known%20as%20the%203-4-5%20program%20%E2%80%94%20three%20nights%20in%20a%20hotel%2C%20four%20days%20at%20a%20client%20site%2C%20and%20a%20fifth%20day%20back%20in%20the%20office.%20I%20flew%20to%20a%20client%20site%20every%20Monday%2C%20stayed%20through%20Wednesday%20night%2C%20and%20flew%20back%20to%20Boston%20on%20Thursday.%20It%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconsulting-has-a-gen-z-problem-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewasn't%20a%20good%20work-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20worked%20on%20three%20significant%20projects%20during%20my%20two%20years%20at%20Deloitte.%20Being%20between%20projects%20was%20called%20being%20%26quot%3Bon%20the%20beach%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20could%20hurt%20your%20utilization%20ratio%2C%20affecting%20raises%20and%20bonuses.%20We%20were%20expected%20to%20find%20projects%20to%20stay%20busy%20with%2C%20so%20I%20took%20on%20initiatives%20for%20the%20company%20like%20volunteering%20and%20writing%20white%20papers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20hustle%2C%20churn-and-burn%20culture%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmckinsey-consultant-quit-mental-health-shattered-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eit%20was%20exhausting%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20hated%20it%2C%20but%20was%20too%20shy%20to%20r