a%20replacement%20and%20in%20October%202010%2C%20at%2024%20years%20old%2C%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fquit-6-figure-job-deloitte-consulting-start-coaching-business-tiktok-2021-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eleft%20Deloitte%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225b2a248b-3bbc-446e-8ce7-cb807bbb3489%5C%22%3EThe%20fear%20of%20having%20to%20return%20to%20finance%20motivated%20me%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20eight-week%20notice%20period%2C%20I%20created%20a%20website%2C%20posted%20on%20social%20media%2C%20and%20gave%20out%20business%20cards%20at%20marketing%20and%20networking%20events%20on%20the%20Fridays%20and%20Saturdays%20I%20was%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20made%20soft%20announcements%20to%20friends.%20Some%20were%20supportive%20and%20immediately%20referred%20me%20to%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20but%20others%20warned%20that%20I'd%20wasted%20my%20college%20education%20and%20that%20photography%20should%20stay%20a%20hobby%20or%20a%20side%20hustle.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20actually%20didn't%20tell%20my%20parents%20for%20the%20first%20couple%20of%20years.%20They'd%20worked%20so%20hard%20that%20for%20me%20to%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20I'm%20going%20to%20leave%20my%20very%20comfortable%2C%20stable%20job%20with%20benefits%20and%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Finvesting%2Fbest-retirement-plans%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretirement%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20do%20my%20own%20thing%26quot%3B%20was%20terrifying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20gave%20myself%20two%20years%20to%20replace%20my%20Deloitte%20salary.%20If%20I%20couldn't%20achieve%20this%2C%20I'd%20return%20to%20another%20corporate%20job%20and%20keep%20photography%20as%20a%20hobby.%20The%20fear%20of%20needing%20to%20return%20to%20finance%20if%20I%20couldn't%20make%20this%20work%20was%20a%20really%20strong%20motivator.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20me%20several%20months%20to%20get%20my%20first%20clients.%20To%20get%20my