that%20platform%20saw%20the%20number%20of%20VCs%20posting%20daily%20on%20X%20halved.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmarenbannon%2F%3ForiginalSubdomain%3Duk%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMaren%20Bannon%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20January%20Ventures%20hasn't%20posted%20on%20X%20in%20a%20year%2C%20despite%20having%20many%20thousands%20of%20followers%2C%20because%20she%20said%20the%20%26quot%3BROI%26quot%3B%20of%20posting%20is%20unclear.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20become%20more%20active%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%26quot%3B%20Bannon%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20that's%20where%20the%20people%20I%20want%20to%20reach%20are%20spending%20time.%26quot%3B%20She's%20not%20the%20only%20one.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20venture%20capitalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fhpierrejacques%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHenri%20Pierre-Jacques%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20used%20to%20tweet%20twice%20a%20day%20but%20dialed%20it%20back%20last%20year.%20He%20noticed%20that%20his%20tweets%20weren't%20getting%20as%20much%20traction%20after%20X%20pushed%20an%20update%20so%20that%20when%20people%20open%20the%20app%2C%20they%20see%20a%20stream%20of%20tweets%20from%20people%20they%20don't%20follow.%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20post%20nearly%20as%20much%20on%20Twitter%20anymore%20because%20it's%20not%20worth%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Pierre-Jacques%20said.%20(He%20still%20posts%20often.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20LinkedIn%2C%20Pierre-Jacques%2C%20a%20managing%20director%20of%20Harlem%20Capital%2C%20shares%20a%20hodgepodge%20of%20fund%20news%2C%20career%20advice%2C%20and%20family%20photos.%20His%20recent%20accounting%20of%20what%20he's%20learned%20from%20the%20billionaires%20in%20his%20network%20garnered%201%2C100%20likes%20and%2096%20comments.%20%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20go%20to%20Twitter%20for%20big%20reach%2C%20now%20I%20go%20to%20LinkedIn%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20is%20where%20the%20major%20links%20of%20the%20funding%20food%