2032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20equity%20market%20cap%20vs%20world%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792cedd10c98eace913bf4b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22984%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESociete%20Generale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20the%20tech%20sector's%20dominance%20within%20the%20US.%20IT%20stocks%20make%20up%2035%25%20of%20the%20market's%20value%2C%20exceeding%20levels%20seen%20during%20the%20dot-com%20bubble%20peak%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221650%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22us%20it%20sector%20market%20cap%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792cf0bae09223df2bb53d9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221090%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESociete%20Generale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EInvestor%20exuberance%20is%20also%20at%20its%20highest%20levels%20in%20at%20least%20the%20last%2040%20years.%20The%20Conference%20Board's%20gauge%20on%20investor%20optimism%20(red)%2C%20which%20historically%20tracks%20with%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20price%20movements%2C%20is%20well%20ahead%20of%20where%20the%20market%20sits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222118%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22conference%20board%20equity%20market%20optimism%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6792cf7410c98eace913bf62%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221008%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESociete%20Generale%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20extreme%20high%20in%20US%20households'%20optimism%20on%20the%20equity%20outlook%20is%20a%20clear%20sign%20of%20froth%2C%20especially%20as%20that%20optimism%20has%20run%20well%20ahead%20of%20price%20performance%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BNormally%20any%20divergence%20occurs%20%3Cem%3Eafter%3C%2Fem%3E%20recessions%20where%20a%20price%20rebound%20from%20bear%20market%20lows%20has%20little%20impact%20on%20still%20shell-shocked%20investor%20sentiment%2C%20eg%202021%20%26amp%3B%202010%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20the%20emphasis%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20around%20why%20stocks%20will%20continue%20to%20outperform%20may%20prove%20plausible.%20As%20companies%20adopt%20AI%20technology%20in%20the%20years%20ahead%2C%20their%20profits%20could%20very%20well%20grow%20robustly.%20How%20things%20actually%20play%20out%2C%20and%20whether%20reality%20can%20live%20up%20to%20investors'%20high%20expectations%2C%20remains%20to%20be%20seen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEither%20way%2C%20Edwards%20isn't%20buying%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20own%20extremely%20jaundiced%20view%20of%20US%20equity%20market%20exceptionalism%20is%20born%20from%20decades%20of%20hearing%20similar%20beguiling%20stories%2C%20be%20it%20the%20Nasdaq%20bubble%20in%20the%20late%201990s%20or%20before%20that%20the%20Asian%20economic%20'miracle'%20of%20the%20mid-1990s%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BEach%20and%20every%20bubble%20has%20a%20compelling%20narrative%20that%20only%20in%20retrospect%20is%20exposed%20as%20nonsense%20%E2%80%94%20most%20recently%20the%202008%20Global%20Financial%20Crisis%20where%20the%20consensus%20view%20was%20that%20there%20was%20no%20bubble%20to%20burst.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BEach%20and%20every%20bubble%20ends%20badly%2C%20and%20this%20one%20will%20be%20no%20different.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEdwards%20is%20regularly%20bearish%2C%20and%20he%20has%20consistently%20highlighted%20downside%20risks%20as%20the%20stock%20market%20has%20continued%20on%20its%20historic%20advance%20over%20the%20last%20couple%20of%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20warnings%20fall%20well%20outside%20of%20market%20consensus%2C%20with%20the%20median%202025%20year-end%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20price%20target%20among%20top%20Wall%20Street%20strategists%20at%206%2C600%20(7.8%25%20upside%20from%20current%20levels).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20arguments%20on%20where%20stock%20valuations%20sit%2C%20especially%20in%20the%20tech%20sector%2C%20and%20how%20much%20they%20rhyme%20with%20periods%20like%20the%20dot-com%20peak%2C%20should%20give%20investors%20something%20to%20consider.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20market%20once%20shrugged%20off%20his%20Nikkei%20index%20and%20dot-com%20bubble%20warnings%20once%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20keep%20a%20copy%20of%20my%201989%20research%20note%20handy%20in%20which%20I%20stressed%20that%20a%20sky-high%20Japanese%20bond%2Fequity%20earnings%20yield%20ratio%20signaled%20that%20the%20Nikkei%20bubble%20was%20about%20to%20pop%2C%26quot%3B%20Edwards%20wrote.%20%26quot%3BBack%20then%20investors%20were%20angry%20that%20I%20even%20dared%20suggest%20such%20a%20thing%20could%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-tech-dot-com-bubble-socgen-edwards-2025-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737798603000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661030981caec1275a6d4eea%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-tech-dot-com-bubble-socgen-edwards-2025-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEach%20and%20every%20bubble%20ends%20badly%2C%20and%20this%20one%20will%20be%20no%20different%2C%26quot%3B%20warns%20Albert%20Edwards.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22wedwards%40businessinsider.com%20(William%20Edwards)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A20%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-crash-ai-tech-dot-com-bubble-socgen-edwards-2025-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rohit%20Sharma%20captain%2C%20four%20Indians%20in%20ICC%20Men's%20T20I%20Team%20of%20the%20Year%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737798509000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117550934%2Cimgsize-38766.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%