%20plan%2C%20post%20the%20release%20of%20the%20four%20Israeli%20women%20soldiers%2C%20Israel%20should%20free%20a%20group%20of%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20although%20the%20exact%20number%20has%20not%20been%20specified%20by%20either%20side.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20fragile%20deal%20is%20set%20to%20build%20the%20foundation%20for%20a%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20ceasefire%20announcement%2C%20many%20displaced%20Gazans%20tried%20to%20go%20back%20home%20after%20more%20than%20a%20year%20of%20incessant%20war%2C%20but%20they%20only%20found%20rubble%20in%20place%20of%20where%20the%20houses%20once%20stood.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20we%20thought%20about%20returning%2C%20there%20is%20no%20place%20for%20us%20to%20put%20our%20tents%20because%20of%20the%20destruction%2C%26quot%3B%20Theqra%20Qasem%2C%20a%20displaced%20woman%2C%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ceasefire%20announcement%20has%20been%20made%20a%20reality%20through%20the%20efforts%20of%20three%20countries%3A%20Qatar%2C%20Egypt%20and%20the%20United%20States%20after%20months%20of%20negotiation.%20However%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20claimed%20full%20credit%20for%20the%20ceasefire%20deal%2C%C2%A0%E2%80%9CThis%20EPIC%20ceasefire%20agreement%20could%20have%20only%20happened%20as%20a%20result%20of%20our%20Historic%20Victory%20in%20November%26quot%3B%2C%20as%20he%20posted%20on%20his%20Truth%20Social%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20first%2042-day%20phase%20of%20the%20ceasefire%20deal%2C%2033%20hostages%20Israel%20believes%20are%20still%20alive%20should%20be%20returned%20in%20exchange%20for%201900%20Palestinian%20prisoners%20held%20in%20Israeli%20jails.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20more%20permanent%20end%20to%20the%20war%20is%20expected%20in%20the%20next%20phase%20of%20the%20war%2C%20and%20the%20last%20phase%20should%20see%20the%20reconstruction%20of%20Gaza%20and%20the%20return%20of%20the%20bodies%20of%20dead%20hostages.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22publi