ool-college%20but%20when%20things%20didn't%20work%20out%2C%20the%20environment%20lover%20decided%20to%20create%20a%20forest.%20And%20then%20began%20the%20arduous%20journey%20of%20planting%20trees%2C%20bringing%20water%2C%20nurturing%20plants%20and%20proving%20villagers%20that%20a%20barren%20hill%20too%20can%20be%20a%20home%20to%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E74-year-old%20Dr%20Garg%20began%20by%20planting%20neem%2C%20peepal%20and%20lemon%20trees.%20Gradually%2C%20the%20number%20and%20variety%20of%20trees%20increased%20and%20in%20eight%20years%20(July%202016%20to%20August%202024)%2C%20Dr%20Garg%20planted%2040%2C000%20trees%20of%20more%20than%20500%20species%20on%20rocks%20and%20stones.%20This%20includes%20Kalpvraksh%20(Tree%20of%20Heaven)%2C%20Saffron%2C%20Rudraksh%2C%20Apple%2C%20Dragon%2C%20Olives%2C%20Lichi%2C%20African%20Tulips%2C%20and%20Cardamom%20Flowers%2C%20among%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeshar%20Parvat%20also%20hosts%20wood%20trees%20including%20Teakwood%2C%20Rosewood%2C%20Sandalwood%2C%20Mahogani%2C%20Banyan%2C%20Sal%2C%20Anjan%2C%20Bamboo%2C%20Willow%2C%20Deodar%2C%20Pine%2C%20Dahiman%2C%20Khamar%2C%20and%20Silver%20Oak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E15%2C000%20trees%20are%20over%2012%20feet%20tall.%20The%20plants%20at%20Keshar%20Parvat%20boast%20a%20survival%20rate%20of%2095%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeither%20of%20these%20plants%20is%20supplied%20with%20additional%20fertiliser.%20The%20nitrogen%20and%20sulphur%20present%20in%20rainwater%20fulfills%20plants'%20requirements%2C%20said%20Dr%20Garg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeshar%20Parvat%20derives%20its%20name%20from%20Saffron%2C%20a%20plant%20native%20to%20Kashmir's%20mountains.%20In%202021%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%2025%20saffron%20flowers%20bloomed%20in%20the%20forest.%20The%20number%20gradually%20rose%20to%20100%20in%202022%20and%20increased%20by%20five-fold%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F2354mfc_saffron-flowers_625x300_25_January_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20learnt%20the%20technique%20of%20how%20to%20grow%20saffron%20in%20a%20hot%20place%20having%20a%20temperature%2043%20degrees%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Dr%20Garg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20about%20the%20secret%2C%20Dr%20Garg%20said%2C%20he%20controls%20ground%20temperature%20by%20giving%20cold%20water%20to%20the%20plants.%20Shady%20conditions%20were%20created%20and%20the%20temperature%20is%20maintained%20around%2018%20degrees%20during%20the%20day%20and%205%20degrees%20at%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20wish%20that%20fragrance%20and%20beauty%20of%20Keshar%20Parvat%20spreads%20everywhere%20just%20like%20Saffron%2C%20the%20Red%20Gold%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20just%20temperature%2C%20Dr%20Garg%20was%20also%20faced%20with%20the%20water%20crisis.%20The%20team%20dug%20three%20bores%20at%20600%20feet%20but%20the%20search%20for%20water%20ended%20in%20a%20dry%20pit.%20Therefore%2C%20water%20tankers%20were%20purchased%20to%20irrigate%20the%20fields.%20Later%2C%20a%20pond%20was%20built%20to%20collect%20water.%20The%20same%20water%20is%20supplied%20to%20plants%20through%20drip%20irrigation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EMore%20Than%20Plants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flora%20has%20attracted%20fauna.%20The%20dense%20forest%20is%20home%20to%2030%20types%20of%20birds%2C%2025%20types%20of%20butterflies%20and%20wild%20animals%20like%20Jackal%2C%20Neel%20Gai%2C%20Rabbits%2C%20Scorpion%2C%20Wild%20Pigs%2C%20and%20Hyena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeshar%20Parvat%20offers%20free%20entry%20to%20visitors.%20It%20has%20a%20conference%20cum%20meditation%20hall%3B%20a%20sensory%20garden%20and%20a%20cricket%20ground%20for%20children%20with%20disabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ED