ss%20Insider%20put%20forth%20a%20list%20of%20options%20that%20included%20changes%20to%20education%20programs%20that%20could%20appear%20in%20a%20coming%20spending%20bill.%20It%20suggested%20repealing%20Biden's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-borrowers-cheaper-payments-debt-cancellation-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESAVE%20income-driven%20repayment%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20repealing%20regulations%20that%20allowed%20for%20debt%20relief%20for%20defrauded%20borrowers%2C%20and%20limiting%20eligibility%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-pslf-borrowers-getting-debt-cancellation-biden-relief-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPublic%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20memo%20also%20proposed%20allowing%20borrowers%20who%20default%20on%20their%20student%20loans%20to%20be%20eligible%20for%20a%20second%20%26quot%3Brehabilitation%20loan%2C%26quot%3B%20which%20would%20allow%20borrowers%20to%20exit%20default%20by%20making%20nine%20payments.%20The%20law%20only%20allows%20borrowers%20to%20rehabilitate%20their%20loans%20once.%20It%20also%20suggested%20reforming%20the%20Pell%20Grant%20to%20expand%20its%20eligibility%20to%20short-term%20credential%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20budget%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbudget.house.gov%2Fimo%2Fmedia%2Fdoc%2Freverse_the_curse_budget_blueprint_fy25-341.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eblueprint%3C%2Fa%3E%20prepared%20by%20GOP%20members%20on%20the%20budget%20committee%20pledged%20to%20stop%20Biden's%20%26quot%3Bstudent%20loan%20bailout%2C%26quot%3B%20saying%20that%20%26quot%3Bour%20budget%20resolution%20stops%20all%20forms%20of%20these%20unconstitutional%2C%20inflationary%2C%20and%20regressive%20student%20loan%20debt%20cancellations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20concluded%20his%20term%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-final-student-loan-forgiveness-action-debt-relief-borrowers-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinal%20week%20of%20targeted%20student-debt%20relief%3C%2Fa%3E%20measures%20for%20borrowers.%20He%20announced%20targeted%20relief%20for%20thousands%20of%20nonprofit%20and%20government%20workers%2C%20those%20with%20total%20and%20permanent%20disabilities%2C%20and%20those%20the%20Education%20Department%20found%20were%20defrauded%20by%20their%20schools%2C%20bringing%20total%20relief%20under%20Biden%20to%20%24188.8%20billion%20for%205.3%20million%20borrowers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Education%20Department%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20from%20Business%20Insider%20on%20Trump's%20priorities%20for%20higher%20education%20and%20student-loan%20borrowers.%20However%2C%20Trump%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-cheaper-student-loan-payments-trump-debt-relief-biden-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreviously%20been%20critical%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Biden's%20debt%20relief%20efforts%2C%20and%20it's%20likely%20his%20administration%20would%20support%20GOP%20legislation%20to%20curb%20Biden's%20expanded%20relief%20and%20repayment%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERep.%20Tim%20Walberg%2C%20chair%20of%20the%20House%20education%20committee%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20he%20remains%20%26quot%3Bcommitted%20to%20helping%20address%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20college%20tuition.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRepublicans%20are%20committed%20to%20pursuing%20policies%20that%20will%20lower%20the%20cost%20of%20college%20and%20protect%20students%20and%20taxpayers%20from%20colleges%20and%20universities%20that%20offer%20degrees%20that%20aren't%20worth%20the%20cost%2C%26quot%3B%20Walberg%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e3fa680-960f-4ea8-be2f-8f68efad469b%5C%22%3EGOP%20higher%20education%20plans%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20GOP%20memo%20said%20that%20eliminating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-borrowers-apply-income-driven-repayment-save-plan-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20SAVE%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20streamlining%20other%20income-driven%20repayment%20plans%20would%20save%20%24127.3%20billion%20over%20a%20decade.%20The%20SAVE%20plan%2C%20first%20introduced%20in%202023%2C%20was%20intended%20to%20make%20monthly%20student-loan%20payments%20cheaper%20with%20a%20shorter%20timeline%20for%20loan%20forgiveness.%20The%20plan%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-plan-blocked-student-loan-company-mohela-debt-cancellation-biden-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efaced%20lawsuits%20from%20GOP-led%20states%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20enrolled%20borrowers%20are%20on%20forbearance%20as%20they%20await%20a%20final%20court%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepealing%20Biden's%20regulations%20making%20it%20easier%20for%20borrowers%20who%20the%20government%20determined%20were%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-art-institutes-borrower-defense-debt-cancellation-biden-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefrauded%20by%20their%20colleges%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20get%20loan%20forgiveness%20is%20also%20among%20the%20GOP's%20suggestions.%20The%20memo%20said%20this%20would%20save%20a%20total%20of%20%2414.6%20billion%20over%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20memo%20proposed%20ending%20interest%20capitalization%2C%20which%20is%20when%20unpaid%20interest%20is%20tacked%20onto%20a%20borrower's%20principal%20balance%2C%20causing%20their%20overall%20debt%20load%20to%20surge.%20This%20is%20an%20idea%20that%20Democratic%20lawmakers%20have%20voiced%20support%20for%2C%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20ideas%20have%20been%20previously%20floated%20in%20GOP%20legislation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgop-bill-overhaul-student-loan-repayment-stop-debt-relief-foxx-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20College%20Cost%20Reduction%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20introduced%20by%20GOP%20Rep.%20Virginia%20Foxx%20last%20January%2C%20outlined%20various%20priorities%20that%20included%20capping%20certain%20forms%20of%20financial%20aid%20and%20limiting%20the%20education%20secretary's%20authority%20to%20implement%20new%20relief%20and%20repayment%20programs.%20The%20legislation%20would%20help%20ensure%20students%20do%20not%20take%20on%20debt%20they%20cannot%20afford%2C%20Foxx%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStudent-loan%20debt%20is%20skyrocketing%2C%20and%20completion%20rates%20are%20plummeting.%20There's%20bipartisan%20agreement%20that%20lasting%20reforms%20are%20needed%20to%20correct%20course%2C%26quot%3B%20Foxx%20told%20BI%20after%20the%20bill%20was%20introduced%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Republicans%20hold%20control%20over%20Congress%2C%20their%20proposals%20are%20still%20likely%20to%20face%20pushback%20from%20Democratic%20lawmakers.%20Democrats%20on%20the%20House's%20education%20committee%20introduced%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdemocrats-edworkforce.house.gov%2Fissues%2Froadmap-to-college-student-success%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eroad%20map%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20higher%20education%20affordability%20last%20year%2C%20which%20included%20a%20range%20of%20legislation%20that%20addressed%20financial%20transparency%20and%20making%20relief%20easier%20through%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20borrowers%20are%20still%20waiting%20to%20hear%20more%20from%20Trump%20and%20lawmakers%20on%20any%20changes%20that%20could%20be%20implemented.%20Trump%20and%20some%20Republicans%20have%20even%20supported%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-musk-ramaswamy-reading-literacy-scores-eliminate-education-department-trump-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egetting%20rid%20of%20the%20Education%20Department%3C%2Fa%3E%20altogether%2C%20but%20doing%20so%20would%20be%20operationally%20complicated%20and