%3EIt%20also%20ran%20through%20Anji%20Khad%20bridge%20-%20which%20is%20India's%20first%20cable-stayed%20railway%20bridge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20train%20briefly%20halted%20at%20Jammu%20around%2011%3A30%20am%20where%20it%20was%20welcomed%20with%20slogans%20and%20praises%20for%20the%20Indian%20Railways.%20It%20then%20moved%20to%20the%20next%20Budgam%20station%20to%20complete%20its%20trial%20run.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommercial%20operations%20of%20the%20train%20are%20set%20to%20begin%20soon%2C%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20expected%20to%20flag%20off%20the%20first%20journey%20from%20Katra.%20The%20date%20of%20the%20flagging-off%20ceremony%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpecial%20features%20of%20the%20train%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Vande%20Bharat%20train%20is%20designed%20to%20operate%20seamlessly%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20challenging%20winter%20conditions%20and%20has%20special%20climate-related%20features.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20the%20other%20Vande%20Bharat%20Express%20trains%20running%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country%2C%20this%20train%20has%20several%20additional%20features%20to%20meet%20operational%20challenges%20and%20passengers'%20needs.%20It%20includes%20advanced%20heating%20systems%20that%20prevent%20the%20freezing%20of%20water%20and%20bio-toilet%20tanks%2C%20provide%20warm%20air%20for%20the%20vacuum%20system%2C%20and%20ensure%20optimal%20functioning%20of%20the%20air-brake%20system%20for%20smooth%20operations%20even%20in%20sub-zero%20temperatures.%20The%20train%20also%20features%20embedded%20heating%20elements%20in%20the%20windshield%20to%20automatically%20defrost%20the%20driver's%20front%20lookout%20glass%2C%20ensuring%20clear%20visibility%20in%20harsh%20winter%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20these%2C%20the%20train%20includes%20other%20amenities%20of%20the%20existing%20Vande%20Bharat%20trains%20such%20as%20fully%20air-conditioned%20coaches%2C%2