t-fiitjee-coaching-centres-7547025%5C%22%3Eclosure%20of%20several%20branches%20of%20FIITJEE%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Delhi%20NCR%20and%20north-India%20has%20left%20hundreds%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Frs-100-crore-in-7-years-fiitjees-old-job-advertisement-with-hefty-salary-resurfaces-amid-crisis-7550573%5C%22%3Eparents%20protesting%20against%20the%20institute%3C%2Fa%3E%20demanding%20refund%20of%20their%20fees.%20The%20crisis%20in%20the%20coaching%20institute%20is%20a%20result%20of%20administrative%20and%20civic%20action%20that%20were%20taken%20against%20its%20branches%20for%20violating%20licensing%20and%20fire%20safety%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20rise%20of%20FIITJEE%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnAs%20per%20the%20information%20shared%20on%20the%20official%20website%2C%20%26quot%3BFIITJEE%20was%20started%20with%20less%20than%20ten%20thousand%20rupees%20in%201992%20and%20it%20became%20a%20leader%20in%20IIT-JEE%20(JEE%20Advanced)%20training%20in%20just%20five%20years%20by%20producing%20not%20just%20All%20India%20Topper%20from%20its%20Long%20Term%20Classroom%20Program%20but%20also%20producing%20Highest%20Selections%20in%20the%20country%20in%201997.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFIITJEE%20was%20created%20by%20D%20K%20Goel%2C%20a%20Mechanical%20Engineering%20graduate%20from%20IIT%20Delhi.%20The%20institute%20was%20initially%20started%20as%20a%20forum%20for%20IIT-JEE%20and%20expanded%20to%2074%20study%20centres%2C%20two%20FIITJEE%20Global%20Schools%2C%20six%20FIITJEE%20World%20Schools%2C%20nine%20FIITJEE%20junior%20colleges%20and%2058%20Associate%20Schools.%20FIITJEE%20centres%20are%20also%20present%20in%20several%20countries%20including%20Bahrain%2C%20Kuwait%2C%20Qatar%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20Oman%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates%2C%20Sri%20Lanka%2C%20Singapore%2C%20Malaysia%2C%20Indonesia%20and%20Nepal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20also%20launched%20FIITJEE%20World%20Schools%20at%20Hyderabad%2C%20and%20also%20FIITJEE%20Global%20School%20at%20Chennai%20and%20Vellore%20in%202021.%20FIITJEE%20Junior%20Colleges%20were%20setup%20in%20Bhubaneswar%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Vijayawada%20and%20Visakhapatnam%20with%20an%20aim%20to%20help%20students%20get%20admission%20to%20IITs%20and%20US%20Universities%20and%20success%20in%20Olympiads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20led%20to%20the%20downfall%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20coaching%20centres%20have%20closed%20in%20cities%20such%20as%20Noida%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Meerut%20and%20Bhopal.%20Parents%20have%20filed%20multiple%20police%20complaints%20in%20these%20regions.%20The%20coaching%20institute's%20reputed%20South%20Delhi%20branch%20at%20Kalu%20Sarai%20near%20IIT-Delhi%20had%20also%20been%20forced%20to%20suspend%20some%20classes%20due%20exit%20of%20teachers%20who%20were%20allegedly%20not%20paid%20wages%20for%20several%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737788520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fa1ldqfg_-fiitjee-greater-noida-centre_625x300_24_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fhistory-of-fiitjee-the-rise-and-downfall-of-the-coaching-institute-7555200%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FIITJEE%20coaching%20centres%20have%20closed%20in%20several%20cities%20such%20as%20Noida%2C%20Ghaziabad%2C%20Meerut%20and%20Bhopal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Who%20is%20Pete%20Hegseth%3F%20The%20new%20Pentagon%20chief%20under%20Donald%20Trump%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737787966000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-117546741%2Cimgsize-999075.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwho-is-pete-hegseth-the-new-pentagon-chief-under-donald-trump%2Farticleshow%2F117546521.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%2