ty-press-secretary-by-donald-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F117545227.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Findian-american-kush-desai-named-white-house-deputy-press-secretary-by-donald-trump%2Famp_articleshow%2F117545227.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Planetary%20Parade%3A%20How%20And%20Where%20To%20See%20This%20Rare%20Celestial%20Event%20In%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EStargazers%20are%20in%20or%20a%20treat%20as%20six%20planets%20-%20Venus%2C%20Mars%2C%20Jupiter%2C%20Saturn%2C%20Neptune%2C%20and%20Uranus%20-%20are%20set%20to%20align%20in%20the%20night%20sky%20today%2C%20January%2025%2C%20offering%20a%20spectacular%20view.%20The%20six%20planets%20will%20form%20an%20astronomical%20alignment%20known%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bplanetary%20parade%26quot%3B.%20This%20celestial%20spectacle%20has%20been%20visible%20for%20most%20of%20the%20month%2C%20beginning%20around%20January%2018%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20through%20early%20February.%20However%2C%20tonight%20all%20the%20six%20planets%20will%20meet%20up%20together%20on%20the%20same%20side%20of%20the%20sun%20in%20a%20wide%20arc%20above%20Earth%20and%20most%20of%20them%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye%20under%20clear%20night%20skies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20NASA%2C%20such%20events%2C%20especially%20those%20involving%20four%20or%20more%20planets%2C%20are%20noteworthy%20and%20do%20not%20occur%20annually.%20Moreover%2C%20what%20makes%20this%20event%20extraordinary%20is%20the%20number%20of%20visible%20bright%20planets%2C%20including%20Mars%2C%20Jupiter%2C%20Saturn%20and%20Venus%2C%20which%20doesn't%20happen%20every%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlanetary%20Parade%3A%20What%20is%20it%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.space.com%2Fstargazing%2Fwatch-planetary-parade-online-for-free-on-jan-25%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESpace.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20planets%20in%20our%20solar%20system%20orbit%20the%20sun%20essentially%20along%20a%20line%20across%20the%20sky%20in%20a%20plane%20called%20the%20ecliptic.%20For%20that%20reason%2C%20planets%20in%20our%20Earthly%20sky%20always%20appear%20somewhere%20along%20a%20line.%20These%20events%2C%20while%20commonplace%2C%20are%20often%20referred%20to%20as%20planetary%20alignments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAstronomers%20say%20that%20while%20tonight's%20event%20might%20be%20overhyped%20as%20some%20type%20of%20%26quot%3Brare%20alignment%2C%26quot%3B%20it's%20actually%20a%20regular%20occurrence%20in%20our%20night%20sky.%20But%20what%20could%20be%20noteworthy%20for%20stargazers%20is%20the%20six%20planets%20that%20will%20be%20visible%20-%20including%20four%20with%20the%20naked%20eye.%20Such%20an%20event%20is%20commonly%20known%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bplanet%20parade%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20NASA%20noted%20that%20the%20moniker%20is%20not%20a%20technical%20astronomical%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlanetary%20Parade%3A%20When%20and%20how%20to%20see%20the%20alignment%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20time%20to%20catch%20the%20event%20is%20about%2045%20minutes%20after%20sunset.%20The%20four%20planets%20-%20Venus%2C%20Mars%2C%20Jupiter%2C%20and%20Saturn%20-%20will%20be%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye%20just%20after%20the%20sun%20goes%20down%2C%20but%20Uranus%20and%20Neptune%20will%20require%20a%20telescope.%20NASA%20stated%20that%20after%20dark%2C%20Venus%20and%20Saturn%20will%20be%20visible%20in%20the%20southwest.%20Jupiter%20will%20shine%20brightly%20overhead%2C%20and%20Mars%20will%20rise%20in%20the%20east.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alignment%20will%20last%20for%20up%20to%20three%20hours%2C%20until%20Venus%20and%20Saturn%20dip%20below%20the%20horizon.%20Venus%20will%20be%20the%20most%20visible%20and%20brightest%20of%20these%20planets.%20Mars%20will%20look%20like%20a%20bright%20lightbulb%20because%20of%20its%20red%20colour.%20Saturn%20will%20appear%20as%20a%20tiny%20dot%20in%20the%20western%20sky%2C%20while%20Jupiter%20will%20also%20be%20similar%20but%20in%20the%20southern%20sky.%20Uranus%20and%20Neptune%20can%20be%20seen%20as%20tiny%2C%20bright%20dots%20but%20will%20not%20be%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye%20due%20to%20their%20distance%20from%20the%20other%20planets%20in%20the%20alignment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlanetary%20Parade%3A%20Visibility%20in%20India%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20planetary%20alignment%20will%20be%20visible%20across%20India.%20Most%20cities%20will%20be%20able%20to%20witness%20this%20rare%20event.%20Venus%2C%20Mars%2C%20Jupiter%2C%20and%20Saturn%20are%20visible%20to%20the%20naked%20eye.%20However%2C%20you%20will%20need%20a%20telescope%20to%20see%20Neptune%20and%20Uranus%2C%20as%20they%20are%20faint.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pathani%20Samant%20Planetarium%20in%20Bhubaneswar%20has%20made%20elaborate%20arrangements%20for%20visitors%2C%20%3Cem%3EPTI%20%3C%2Fem%3Equoted%20an%20official%20as%20saying.%20Visitors%20will%20be%20able%20to%20witness%20the%20rare%20event%20on%20all%20days%2C%20except%20Monday%2C%20from%205.30%20pm%20to%207.30%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Centre%20(TNSTC)%20is%20also%20organising%20a%20special%20night%20sky%20observation%20at%20Kotturpuram-based%20Periyar%20Science%20and%20Technology%20Centre%20from%20January%2022%20to%2025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20to%20offer%20the%20public%20an%20opportunity%20to%20witness%20this%20remarkable%20phenomenon%2C%20the%20Gujarat%20Council%20on%20Science%20and%20Technology%20(GUJCOST)%2C%20under%20the%20Department%20of%20Science%20and%20Technology%20of%20Gujarat%2C%20has%20also%20organised%20a%20series%20of%20public%20observation%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EPlanetary%20Parade%3A%20Ideal%20spot%20to%20witness%20the%20celestial%20event%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChoose%20a%20spot%20with%20an%20unobstructed%20