%20leaves%20of%20doctors%20and%20paramedics%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20medical%20alert%20following%20the%20deaths%20of%2017%20people%20from%20Badhaal%20village%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir's%20Rajouri%20district%20due%20to%20a%20mysterious%20illness.%20The%20number%20of%20people%20sent%20to%20quarantine%20has%20risen%20to%20230.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnion%20minister%20Dr%20Jitendra%20Singh%20said%20the%20initial%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20the%20toxicology%20laboratory%20in%20Lucknow%20concluded%20that%20the%20cause%20was%20not%20any%20infection%2C%20virus%20or%20bacteria%20but%20a%20toxin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrincipal%20of%20Rajouri%20Government%20Medical%20College%20(GMC)%20Hospital%2C%20Dr%20Amarjeet%20Singh%20Bhatia%2C%20on%20Friday%20addressed%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20Rajouri%20and%20announced%20that%20all%20leaves%20of%20doctors%20and%20paramedic%20staff%20have%20been%20cancelled.%20%26quot%3BThe%20winter%20vacations%20have%20also%20been%20cancelled%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20medical%20alert%20situation%20after%2017%20people%20from%20three%20families%20died%20under%20mysterious%20conditions%20in%20the%20last%20one-and-a-half%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20government%20has%20deputed%2010%20additional%20medical%20students%20to%20GMC%20Rajouri%20to%20aid%20the%20medical%20setup%20amid%20the%20ongoing%20health%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20health%20condition%20of%20three%20persons%20undergoing%20treatment%20at%20GMC%20Hospital%20in%20Jammu%20and%20PGI%20Chandigarh%20is%20being%20monitored%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFour%20people%2C%20including%20three%20sisters%2C%20were%20shifted%20to%20hospitals%2C%20with%20three%20airlifted%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Jammu%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20persons%2C%20including%20relatives%20who%20had%20come%20in%20contact%20with%20the%20victim%20families%2C%20were%20sent%20on%20Friday%20to%20quarantine%20as%20a%20precautionary%20measure.%20As%20a%20precaution%2C%20more%20individuals%2C%20including%20close%20relatives%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20have%20been%20relocated%20to%20the%20Nursing%20College%20quarantine%20centre%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20increasing%20the%20number%20to%20230%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStrict%20security%20has%20been%20put%20in%20place%20at%20the%20Nursing%20College%20quarantine%20centre%20in%20Rajouri%2C%20which%20has%20been%20heavily%20secured%20and%20fenced%2C%20they%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20people%20who%20came%20into%20contact%20with%20the%20affected%20families%2C%20from%20taking%20children%20to%20the%20hospital%20to%20burying%20them%2C%20have%20also%20been%20identified%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20minister%20said%20a%20thorough%20investigation%20is%20underway.%20%26quot%3BThe%20initial%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20our%20toxicology%20laboratory%20in%20Lucknow%20concluded%20that%20it%20was%20not%20due%20to%20any%20infection%2C%20virus%20or%20bacteria%20but%20rather%20a%20toxin%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20investigation%20into%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20toxin%20is%20going%20on.%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20long%20series%20of%20toxins%20being%20tested.%20I%20believe%20a%20solution%20will%20be%20found%20soon.%20Additionally%2C%20if%20there%20was%20any%20mischief%20or%20malicious%20activity%2C%20that%20is%20also%20being%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remote%20Badhaal%20village%20was%20declared%20a%20containment%20zone%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20with%20prohibitory%20orders%20imposed%20on%20all%20public%20and%20private%20gatherings%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20deaths%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeventeen%20people%2C%20including%2013%20children%2C%20from%20the%20families%20of%20Mohammad%20Fazal%2C%20Mohammad%20Aslam%20and%20Mohammad%20Rafiq%20in%20Badhaal%20village%20died%20due%20to%20a%20mysterious%20illness%20over%20the%20past%20one-and-a-half%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20the%20central%20team%20and%20police%20are%20continuing%20their%20separate%20probes%20into%20the%20deaths%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20central%20team%20continued%20its%20investigation%20on%20Friday%20into%20the%20cause%20of%20the%20deaths%20which%20occurred%20in%20three%20families.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Special%20Investigation%20Team%20(SIT)%2C%20which%20was%20set%20up%20by%20the%20police%20after%20certain%20neurotoxins%20were%20found%20in%20the%20samples%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20continued%20its%20probe%20into%20the%20criminal%20angle.%20They%20have%20questioned%20over%2050%20people%20in%20this%20case%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Bhatia%20revealed%20that%20the%20common%20factor%20among%20all%2017%20deaths%20is%20the%20involvement%20of%20the%20brain%20and%20damage%20to%20the%20nervous%20system.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737777840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fubnqsqb8_rajouri_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fleaves-of-doctors-cancelled-as-cases-of-mystery-illness-rise-in-j-ks-rajouri-7554233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Authorities%20have%20cancelled%20all%20leaves%20of%20doctors%20and%20paramedics%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20a%20medical%20alert%20following%20the%20deaths%20of%2017%20people%20in%20J%26amp%3BK.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20freezes%20aid%20for%20all%20countries%20including%20Ukraine%2C%20except%20Israel%20and%20Turkey%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737777644000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F