%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20US%20Solicitor%20General%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20not%20clear%20that%20the%20jury's%20verdict%20in%20this%20case-%20which%20involves%20conspiracy%20charges%20and%20was%20somewhat%20difficult%20to%20parse%20-%20means%20that%20he%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bconvicted%20or%20acquitted%26quot%3B%20on%20all%20of%20the%20specific%20conduct%20that%20India%20has%20charged%2C%26quot%3B%20Prelogar%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERana%20is%20known%20to%20be%20associated%20with%20Pakistani-American%20terrorist%20David%20Coleman%20Headley%2C%20one%20of%20the%20main%20conspirators%20of%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20total%20of%20166%20people%2C%20including%20six%20Americans%2C%20were%20killed%20in%20the%202008%20Mumbai%20terror%20attacks%20in%20which%2010%20Pakistani%20terrorists%20laid%20a%20more%20than%2060-hour%20siege%2C%20attacking%20and%20killing%20people%20at%20iconic%20and%20vital%20locations%20of%20Mumbai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737777300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fik9apsg_tahawwur-rana-2008-mumbai-terror-attack-ani_625x300_17_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-supreme-court-clears-26-11-accused-tahawwur-ranas-extradition-to-india-7554096%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20Supreme%20Court%20has%20cleared%20Mumbai-attack%20convict%20Tahawwur%20Rana's%20extradition%20to%20India%20as%20it%20dismissed%20a%20review%20petition%20against%20his%20conviction%20in%20the%20case.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-supreme-court-clears-26-11-accused-tahawwur-ranas-extradition-to-india-7554096%22%2C%22cd