%20for%20her%20personal%20safety.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20affidavit%2C%20Hegseth%20also%20told%20his%20ex-sister-in-law%20that%20women%20should%20not%20work%20or%20have%20the%20right%20to%20vote%2C%20and%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BChristians%20needed%20to%20have%20more%20children%20so%20they%20can%20overtake%20the%20Muslim%20population.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20combative%20confirmation%20hearing%2C%20Hegseth%20stuck%20to%20his%20opposition%20to%20diversity%2C%20equity%20and%20inclusion%20policies%20--%20long%20a%20bugbear%20for%20Republicans%20--%20saying%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdividing%20troops%20inside%20formations%2C%20causing%20commanders%20to%20walk%20on%20eggshells%2C%20not%20putting%20meritocracy%20first.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20sought%20to%20soften%20past%20remarks%20opposing%20women%20serving%20in%20combat%2C%20telling%20lawmakers%20that%20%26quot%3Bwomen%20will%20have%20access%20to%20ground%20combat%20roles...%20given%20the%20standards%20remain%20high.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20more%20of%20Trump's%20most%20contentious%20nominees%20will%20soon%20be%20grilled%20by%20lawmakers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKash%20Patel%20--%20Trump's%20nominee%20to%20lead%20the%20FBI%20--%20Tulsi%20Gabbard%2C%20his%20pick%20for%20director%20of%20national%20intelligence%2C%20and%20Robert%20F%20Kennedy%20Jr%2C%20the%20president's%20choice%20for%20secretary%20of%20health%20and%20human%20services%2C%20are%20expected%20to%20have%20Senate%20hearings%20next%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737776760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F8diivb0o_pete-hegseth_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrumps-controversial-pick-pete-hegseth-confirmed