%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2Fd8ra5is_s_625x300_25_January_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fentertainment%2Fsky-force-box-office-collection-day-1-akshay-kumars-big-comeback-with-double-digit-opening-after-a-string-of-flops-7554142%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20last%20big%20hit%20in%20Akshay%20Kumar's%20career%20was%20Sooryavanshi%20(2021)%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Budget%202025%3A%20How%20Married%20Couples%20Could%20Benefit%20From%20Joint%20Tax%20Filing%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget%202025%2C%20the%20Institute%20of%20Chartered%20Accountants%20of%20India%20(ICAI)%20has%20proposed%20the%20introduction%20of%20joint%20taxation%20for%20married%20couples.%20Under%20joint%20taxation%2C%20a%20married%20couple%20would%20be%20treated%20as%20a%20single%20taxable%20unit%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20combine%20their%20incomes%20when%20filing%20tax%20returns%2C%20similar%20to%20systems%20already%20in%20place%20in%20countries%20like%20the%20US%20and%20the%20UK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BICAI%20suggests%20allowing%20joint%20income%20tax%20return%20filing%20for%20married%20couples%2C%26quot%3B%20Chartered%20Accountant%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20wrote%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20%26quot%3BIdeally%2C%20an%20individual%20income%20of%20Rs%207%20lakh%20is%20exempt%20from%20tax%3B%20if%20married%2C%20the%20exempt%20limit%20for%20the%20family%20would%20be%20Rs%2014%20lakh.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EICAI%20suggests%20allowing%20joint%20income%20tax%20return%20filing%20for%20married%20couples.%20Ideally%2C%20an%20individual%20income%20of%20%E2%82%B97%20lakh%20is%20exempt%20from%20tax%3B%20if%20married%2C%20the%20exempt%20limit%20for%20the%20family%20would%20be%20%E2%82%B914%20lakh.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWill%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2Fbudget2025%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23budget2025%3C%2Fa%3E%20introduce%20this%20new%20concept%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20CA%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20(%40CAChirag)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCAChirag%2Fstatus%2F1876588595810849196%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJanuary%207%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20proposal%20suggests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICAI%20suggests%20that%20married%20couples%20should%20be%20able%20to%20choose%20between%20filing%20taxes%20individually%20or%20together%20under%20a%20new%20joint%20taxation%20system.%20This%20system%20could%20benefit%20families%20with%20one%20income%20earner%20and%20help%20prevent%20tax%20avoidance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20proposed%20tax%20slabs%20for%20couples%20filing%20jointly%20are%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUp%20to%20Rs%206%20lakh%3A%20No%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%206-14%20lakh%3A%205%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%2014-20%20lakh%3A%2010%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%2020-24%20lakh%3A%2015%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%2024-30%20lakh%3A%2020%20per%20cent%20tax%3Cbr%3E%5CnAbove%20Rs%2030%20lakh%3A%2030%20per%20cent%20tax%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20joint%20filing%20system%2C%20the%20basic%20exemption%20limit%20would%20be%20doubled%20to%20Rs%206%20lakh%20from%20the%20current%20Rs%203%20lakh.%20The%20ICAI%20also%20recommends%20raising%20the%20surcharge%20threshold%20from%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20to%20Rs%201%20crore.%20The%20surcharge%20would%20apply%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERs%201%20crore%20to%20Rs%202%20crore%3A%2010%20per%20cent%20surcharge%3Cbr%3E%5CnRs%202%20crore%20to%20Rs%204%20crore%3A%2015%20per%20cent%20surcharge%3Cbr%3E%5CnAbove%20Rs%204%20crore%3A%2025%20per%20cent%20surcharge%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBoth%20partners%20in%20a%20salaried%20couple%20would%20also%20benefit%20fr