hat%20he%20called%20%26quot%3Bradical%26quot%3B%20affirmative%20action%20in%20awarding%20federal%20contracts%2C%20revoking%20an%20order%20crafted%20to%20combat%20racism%20that%20dates%20back%20to%20the%20civil%20rights%20era%20of%20the%201960s.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20also%20promised%20to%20sweep%20away%20policies%20supporting%20transgender%20people%2C%20insisting%20that%20the%20United%20States%20will%20officially%20recognize%20only%20two%20genders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20earlier%20orders%20also%20required%20federal%20department%20and%20agency%20bosses%20to%20ask%20%26quot%3Bemployees%20if%20they%20know%20of%20any%20efforts%20to%20disguise%20these%20(DEI)%20programs%20by%20using%20coded%20or%20imprecise%20language.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737772200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-01%2F57ijm1pg_donald-trump_625x300_25_January_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-administration-directs-us-agencies-to-start-firing-diversity-staff-7553748%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20administration%20of%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20on%20Friday%20directed%20federal%20agencies%20to%20start%20terminating%20staffers%20working%20in%20positions%20related%20to%20diversity%20programs%2C%20after%20placing%20them%20on%20paid%20leave%20earlier%20this%20week.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Gaza%20rescuers%20face%20toll%20of%20their%20work%3A%20'I%20have%20become%20afraid%20of%20my%20own%20memories'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1737769939000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F6be4%2Flive%2F6f61e770-d96b-11ef-902e-cf9b84dc1357.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22htt