itzerland.%20They%20thought%20he%20was%20lying%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20entrepreneur%20adds.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20he%20started%20posting%20pictures%20and%20videos%20on%20Instagram%2C%20his%20friends%20finally%20believed%20him.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20impact%20of%20this%20experience%20was%20evident%20not%20only%20in%20the%20children%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20but%20in%20their%20future%20prospects.%20Two%20of%20the%20five%20students%20from%20the%20team%20went%20on%20to%20receive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F269061%2Fleena-nair-chanel-ceo-unilever-kolhapur-maharastra-london-inspiring%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eadmissions%20into%20top%20engineering%20colleges%3C%2Fa%3E.%20These%20students%2C%20once%20overlooked%20and%20underestimated%2C%20are%20now%20role%20models%20for%20other%20government%20school%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EShaping%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20problem-solvers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20TIS%20is%20working%20on%20the%20%E2%80%98Nurturing%20Innovators%E2%80%99%20programme%2C%20which%20has%20become%20a%20key%20initiative%20in%20shaping%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20problem-solvers.%20Through%20this%20programme%2C%20private%20school%20students%20are%20encouraged%20to%20identify%20real-world%20challenges%20and%20design%20technological%20solutions%20to%20address%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20notable%20example%20comes%20from%20a%20student%20who%20realised%20that%20government%20hospitals%20are%20often%20understaffed%20and%20it%20is%20difficult%20to%20cater%20to%20every%20bed.%20%E2%80%9CShe%20observed%20that%20when%20an%20IV%20drip%20was%20missing%20from%20any%20bed%2C%20there%20was%20no%20immediate%20way%20for%20the%20hospital%20staff%20to%20be%20alerted%2C%E2%80%9D%20Meenal%20explains.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20inspired%20her%20to%20design%20a%20device%20that%20would%20notify%20the%20central%20monitoring%20unit