%20is%20the%20Nirikhyana%20app%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Berhampur%20Sub-Collector%20Dheenah%20Dastageer%20IAS%2C%20stressing%20its%20role%20in%20overcoming%20socioeconomic%20barriers%20and%20the%20digital%20divide.%20She%20also%20assisted%20the%20team%20in%20designing%20the%20mobile%20app%20and%20its%20implementation%20at%20the%20grassroots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20district%20follows%20a%20three-module%20approach%20that%20allows%20Auxiliary%20Nurse%20Midwives%20(ANMs)%20to%20register%20pregnant%20women%20on%20the%20Nirikhyana%20mobile%20app%2C%20facilitating%20consultations%20with%20doctors%20who%20can%20then%20refer%20cases%20to%20nearby%20ultrasound%20clinics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDibyajyoti%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20structured%20three-tier%20system%20approach%20allows%20for%20the%20proactive%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F325599%2Fmadurai-jiovio-healthcare-startup-pregnancy-risk-monitoring-device-rural-women-infant-mortality%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eidentification%20of%20high-risk%20pregnancies%20%3C%2Fa%3Eat%20least%2020%20to%2025%20days%20before%20the%20due%20date.%20This%20allows%20us%20to%20enable%20timely%20interventions%20and%20treatment%20that%20significantly%20help%20us%20reduce%20maternal%20deaths%2C%20still-births%2C%20and%20child%20mortality%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUltrasounds%20are%20no%20longer%20a%20%E2%80%98rich%20person%E2%80%99s%20thing%E2%80%99!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20the%20most%20groundbreaking%20aspect%20of%20the%20initiative%20is%20making%20ultrasounds%20free.%20%E2%80%9CIn%20a%20patriarchal%20society%2C%20spending%20on%